'''J<U+00F3>zef Spors''' (June 13, 1941-1992) was a [[Poland|Polish]] [[historian]], specializing in the medieval [[History of Poland]] and its northern region - [[Pomerania]].

== Biography ==
Spors was born in [[Toru<U+0144>]] in 1941, during [[German occupation of Poland]]. He studied [[history]] at the [[Nicolaus Copernicus University in Toru<U+0144>]]. He graduated in 1965 after presnting thesis concerning [[Margraviate of Brandenburg|Brandenburg]] expansion into Polish lands in the 13th century. His Ph.D. thesis concerned political history of the [[Land of S<U+0142>upsk-S<U+0142>awno]] and the region of [[Bia<U+0142>ogarda]] in the 13th and 14th centuries. He received his postdoctoral after publishing a disertation concerning administrative divisions of [[Gda<U+0144>sk Pomerania]] and the [[Land of S<U+0142>upsk-S<U+0142>awno]] from 12th to 14th century.

During his short life he published over 80 publications including 6 historical monographies. Another 20 were published after his death. His main field of interest was history of both [[Farther Pomerania|Western]] and Gda<U+0144>sk Pomerania. However his works concentrated on the history of the whole of [[Medieval Poland]] as well.

He was the founder and first director of the Institute of history at the Pomeranian Academy in [[S<U+0142>upsk]] from 1986 to 1991.

== Publications ==
* ''Dzieje polityczne ziemi s<U+0142>upskiej, s<U+0142>awie<U+0144>skiej i bia<U+0142>ogardzkiej w XII-XIVw'' (1973)
* ''Agresja Brandenburska wobec Polski do 1278 roku.'' (1973)
* ''Podzia<U+0142> dzielnicowy Polski wed<U+0142>ug statutu Boles<U+0142>awa Krzywoustego ze szczeg<U+00F3>lnym uwzgl<U+0119>dnieniem dzielnicy seniorackiej.'' (1978)
* ''Podzia<U+0142>y administracyjne Pomorza Gda<U+0144>skiego i S<U+0142>awie<U+0144>sko-s<U+0142>upskiego od XII do pocz<U+0105>tku XIV w.'' (1983)
* ''Studia nad wczesno<U+015B>redniowiecznymi dziejami Pomorza Zachodniego. XII - pierwsza po<U+0142>owa XIII w.'' (1988)
* ''Wojewodowie Polski dzielnicowej w XII i XIII wieku. cz. I'' (1991)
* ''Uwagi nad genez<U+0105> wojewody dzielnicowego w Polsce XII - pocz<U+0105>tku XIII wieku.'' (1991)
* ''Organizacja kasztela<U+0144>ska na Pomorzu Zachodnim'' (1991)

